name: String Methods
body:
# Welcome to our project.

Below, you will find links to the outline of the project, the rubric and some help from us.

Remember that your goal is to find the value of the _string_ and compare it. Give out all your results in percentiles. Look at the **help** file for more information and tips!

#### Goodluck.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
